\f1\b0 When Jesus looked up and saw a great crowd coming toward him, he said to Philip, \'93Where shall 
\f2\i\b we
\f1\i0\b0  buy bread for these people to eat?\'94 \cf2 \strokec2 \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl1\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 I believe this is one if not the first time \'93WE\'94 is mentioned when it comes to a miracle.\uc0\u8232 \
\ls8\ilvl1\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Normally you read the passages and it says \'91HE\'92 as in Jesus did the miracle but on this one\'85Jesus invited the disciples to be a part of it.\uc0\u8232 \
\ls8\ilvl1\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 This invitation is the core of the tension because Jesus has the POWER but does He have the hearts of his PEOPLE?\uc0\u8232 \
\ls8\ilvl1\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Many times we are great at praying for things and seeing needs but when it comes time to do something and Jesus says - you feed them\'85that\'92s when we back off.\uc0\u8232 \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\partightenfactor0
